batchFillOrKillOrders(address[5][],uint2.details: Synchronously executes multiple fillOrKill orders in a single transaction.

params.fillTakerTokenAmounts: Array of desired amounts of takerToken to fill in orders.
params.orderAddresses: Array of address arrays containing individual order addresses.
params.orderValues: Array of uint arrays containing individual order values.
params.r: Array of ECDSA signature r parameters.
params.s: Array of ECDSA signature s parameters.

batchFillOrders(address[5][],uint256[6][.details: Synchronously executes multiple fill orders in a single transaction.

params.fillTakerTokenAmounts: Array of desired amounts of takerToken to fill in orders.
params.orderAddresses: Array of address arrays containing individual order addresses.
params.orderValues: Array of uint arrays containing individual order values.
params.r: Array of ECDSA signature r parameters.
params.s: Array of ECDSA signature s parameters.
params.shouldThrowOnInsufficientBalanceOrAllowa: Test if transfers will fail before attempting.

fillOrKillOrder(address[5],uint256[6],ui.details: Fills an order with specified parameters and ECDSA signature, throws if specified amount not filled entirely.

params.fillTakerTokenAmount: Desired amount of takerToken to fill.
params.orderAddresses: Array of order's maker, taker, makerToken, takerToken, and feeRecipient.
params.orderValues: Array of order's makerTokenAmount, takerTokenAmount, makerFee, takerFee, expirationTimestampInSec, and salt.

params.fillTakerTokenAmount: Desired amount of takerToken to fill.
params.orderAddresses: Array of order's maker, taker, makerToken, takerToken, and feeRecipient.
params.orderValues: Array of order's makerTokenAmount, takerTokenAmount, makerFee, takerFee, expirationTimestampInSec, and salt.
params.shouldThrowOnInsufficientBalanceOrAllowa: Test if transfer will fail before attempting.

fillOrder(address[5],uint256[6],uint256,.return: Total amount of takerToken filled in trade.

fillOrdersUpTo(address[5][],uint256[6][].details: Synchronously executes multiple fill orders in a single transaction until total fillTakerTokenAmount filled.

params.fillTakerTokenAmount: Desired total amount of takerToken to fill in orders.
params.orderAddresses: Array of address arrays containing individual order addresses.
params.orderValues: Array of uint arrays containing individual order values.
params.r: Array of ECDSA signature r parameters.
params.s: Array of ECDSA signature s parameters.
params.shouldThrowOnInsufficientBalanceOrAllowa: Test if transfers will fail before attempting.

fillOrdersUpTo(address[5][],uint256[6][].return: Total amount of fillTakerTokenAmount filled in orders.

getOrderHash(address[5],uint256[6]).details: Calculates Keccak-256 hash of order with specified parameters.

params.orderAddresses: Array of order's maker, taker, makerToken, takerToken, and feeRecipient.
params.orderValues: Array of order's makerTokenAmount, takerTokenAmount, makerFee, takerFee, expirationTimestampInSec, and salt.

getPartialAmount(uint256,uint256,uint256.details: Calculates partial value given a numerator and denominator.

getUnavailableTakerTokenAmount(bytes32).details: Calculates the sum of values already filled and cancelled for a given order.

params.orderHash: The Keccak-256 hash of the given order.

getUnavailableTakerTokenAmount(bytes32).return: Sum of values already filled and cancelled.

isValidSignature(address,bytes32,uint8,b.details: Verifies that an order signature is valid.
